WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:01.940
Sometimes when you're bootstrapping,

00:00:01.940 --> 00:00:04.710
you don't have access to all
the resources that you need.

00:00:04.710 --> 00:00:05.640
In this situation,

00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:08.830
you could consider debt financing
to help start your business.

00:00:08.830 --> 00:00:11.970
If you choose to do this, there are some
things that you need to be aware of and

00:00:11.970 --> 00:00:14.460
a few financial professionals
that you should consult with.

00:00:14.460 --> 00:00:17.549
So let's hear some of the basics of
debt financing for your business.

